	note = {Cited by: 28; Conference name: 11th International Conference on Learning Analytics and Knowledge: The Impact we Make: The Contributions of Learning Analytics to Learning, LAK 2021; Conference sponsors: ; Conference code: 168184; Conference date: 12 April 2021 through 16 April 2021; All Open Access; Green Open Access}
